0.1.0 - Release

0.1.1 - Added the rest of the rare achievements, added .45 ACP to the Ammo Table.

0.1.2 - Added the rest of all the achievements. Added spacers in the achievement command. Added a "are you sure you want to quit?" input to the quit command.

0.1.3 - Added changelog command, added dev notes in the code for easier organization.

0.1.4 - Bug fix, changed if to elif to fix issues.

0.1.5 - Added item ID converter, added the spt wiki to tools command, added a reccomended mods command, changed title color and added a customizable menu.

0.1.6 - Added more items to the item ID converter, fixed typos, updated UI
